## A few projects:
* [Sudoku Solver](https://github.com/oabm/sudoku-solver)
  * Exploring Sudoku solving algorithms with Scala.
* [Gravity Game](https://github.com/oabm/gravity-game)
  * Learning [Kivy](https://kivy.org).
  * Originally implemented in 2012. Recently migrated to Github.
* [HTML, CSS, and Javascript for Web Developers (__Coursera__)](https://github.com/oabm/coursera-web-dev)
  * Solutions to assignments for [course](https://www.coursera.org/learn/html-css-javascript-for-web-developers).
* [*This* Page](https://github.com/oabm/oabm.github.io)
  * The source code to the page you're viewing _right now_!
